3.
Cookies and Relevant Technologies
Cookies are a neutral technology that allows web servers to store data on or read data from clients. To optimize your experience, we use cookies or similar technologies. We will not use the above technologies for any purpose other than those described in this policy. Please understand that some services can only be achieved by using the above technologies. You can disable or delete the above technologies by changing your settings, or by visiting the provider's web pages, as permitted by your device or associated program. However, this action may affect your use of products and/or services.
4.
Use of Personal Information
We will use the information collected for the purposes covered by this Privacy Policy. If the scope of your personal information we intend to use exceeds the scope described in this "Privacy Policy", we will revise the content of this "Privacy Policy" before collecting your personal information and obtaining your express consent again.
We will strictly abide by the provisions of laws and regulations and the agreement with you, and use the collected information in accordance with this "Privacy Policy" and "User Agreement". We will analyze the operation of this game according to the frequency and situation of your use of the product, error information, and performance information, to ensure the security of the service, optimize our products and improve the quality of our services. We do not combine information stored in analytics software with the personally identifiable information you provide.
5.
Sharing, Transference, and Disclosure of Personal Information
We will strictly abide by relevant laws and keep your personal information secret. We will not sell your personal information to third parties except for the necessary circumstances stipulated by law. We promise not to share or otherwise disclose the personal information that you provide to us or that we collect to third-party service providers, nor collect your personal information on behalf of third-party service providers for them.
6.
Storage of Personal Information
We will retain your personal data for the time needed to provide services to you unless the laws demand we delete it or we have received your request to delete it. In order to protect your personal information, the information that we collect will be stored according to relevant privacy laws and regulations in related countries.
If we cease to provide services or operate, we and the third parties we cooperate with will stop collecting your personal information in time and shall abide by relevant laws and regulations to inform you in advance and delete or anonymize your personal data after we cease to operate or provide services unless there are laws, regulations or regulatory authority that demand otherwise.
7.
Information Security
We have information security and access policies to limit access to our systems and technology. And we protect data through the use of technical safeguards such as encryption. Please note that no data security measures can always guarantee 100% security. You should always be cautious when it comes to your personal information.
8.Your Rights
Access, Update, and Delete Personal Information
We take your rights to manage your personal information very seriously. However, if you choose to delete this information, some features that require such information may no longer be available. If you want to check, modify or delete your personal data in the product, please contact us according to the contact information provided by us. We will verify your identity and make reasonable operations after clarifying your specific needs.
Account Deletion
You can directly contact us via the contact information provided in this privacy policy, at [Settings] - [Account Deletion] or at other places in the product if you wish to delete your product account. When requesting account deletion, we will verify your identity, account security status, and deletion conditions. You may consult our Account Deletion policy for more details. Your personal information involved with this account will be deleted or anonymized upon game account deletion unless the laws and regulations or this privacy policy demand otherwise. Please be reminded that, once deleted, your account will be unrecoverable. User caution is advised.
9.
Minor Protection
We attach great importance to the protection of minors' personal information and are constantly exploring better ways to protect minors' personal information. If you are the legal guardian of a minor, please pay attention to whether the minor under your guardianship is using our products and services or providing their personal information after having obtained your authorization and consent. If you are a minor's guardian and have questions about the services the minor uses or information the minor provides to us, please contact us in time.
10.
Update of This Privacy Policy
In order to provide you with better services, the related services of our products will be updated and changed from time to time. We will also update this Privacy Policy from time to time. These revisions form part of this Privacy Policy and have the same effect as this Privacy Policy. We will not reduce any rights you enjoy in this current effective privacy policy without your express consent. It is strongly recommended that you frequently read this page with reference to the date of the last modification date listed in this Privacy Policy.
11.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us by sending us an email. Our email address is
nightredvovo@163.com
